{"tid":2267922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒：騰訊掌遊戲市場更危險","createTime":"2020-11-02T11:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:26:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8af3c16f36d5ad1760fcad45f16f74c979f7d039","tid":2267922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201102/KKZL3ARCB5HSBD5NQWM26RGHBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201102%2FKKZL3ARCB5HSBD5NQWM26RGHBM%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=7c7b8a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201102%2FKKZL3ARCB5HSBD5NQWM26RGHBM%2F&h=f61ff121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201102/KKZL3ARCB5HSBD5NQWM26RGHBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美媒：騰訊掌遊戲市場更危險<br />\n<br />\n以為只有中國操控的社交媒體才有資料「送中」問題？美國前政府資安專家艾特爾及智庫「新美國安全中心」學者司馬喬丹向《華爾街日報》指出，中國科技巨擘騰訊現時已購入多個著名遊戲開發廠商，以外國人打機時間比用社交媒體更多，認為中國背後操控的遊戲市場更加危險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/l77j0w3nnrxZLb_6bPqkRE8DHos=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BIIBKCG7FZHZRDQEKR47UMQXDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fl77j0w3nnrxZLb_6bPqkRE8DHos%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBIIBKCG7FZHZRDQEKR47UMQXDQ.jpg&h=4a3a7e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■騰訊曾打壓爭取民主的港人選手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料可被存至雲端<br />\n<br />\n這篇文章名為「如果你在打電動遊戲，中國有可能正在監視你」。文章指騰訊現時在遊戲界實力大增，已購入多個開發廠商，包括《魔獸世界》開發商「暴雪」母公司「動視暴雪」、《英雄聯盟》開發商Riot Games，美國電動遊戲社交平台Discord也被收攬。遊戲玩家在電腦安裝遊戲時，竊取資訊就好像透過TikTok拿取用戶資料一樣容易，事關玩家在開始遊戲前，一般都要提供真實姓名、付費賬戶、所在國家，並可透過遊戲安裝的聊天室，偷取用戶的語音資料來製作聲音庫，這些資料有可能被存放在騰訊，甚或是由阿里巴巴的雲端系統。北京更可透過讀取數百萬名玩家的電腦，從中作情報活動。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑對《蘋果》指，........................<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"753bf89bf9caefd022a8be89da44f05cd36ab4b5","tid":2267922,"uid":65743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFXcuQf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFXcuQf.gif&h=0b8c3f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e3724b5416dcd2896025f38e4957c474b314459","tid":2267922,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753bf89bf9caefd022a8be89da44f05cd36ab4b5","tid":2267922,"uid":65743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFXcuQf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFXcuQf.gif&h=0b8c3f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bb955fea86dadb5737875d23173cfffda2f53e","tid":2267922,"uid":115579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"根本就係用低賤嘅勞力同老翻去賺取財富，再文化侵略全世界，有少少歷史常識嘅都知<br />\n<br />\n中國人最鍾意就搞同化，話就話唔打仗，結果買尻哂你全家，而家仲幫埋你種債"},{"pid":"7a520eacfb7c8e55d65c4017e08ae3eb898986cb","tid":2267922,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"支共壯大到一個痴左線嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求神拜佛侵侵贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027975dbafd5516034ac4ec379db8a4152b51e59","tid":2267922,"uid":347528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"八九成都支那game但係冇辦法"},{"pid":"ae8d61c5f83d3986fe37f9cec9cd35625d387e6d","tid":2267922,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"要玩LOL 不了"},{"pid":"3628a7a3480aee466d5b08511af509ec41f64bc7","tid":2267922,"uid":218731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"有咩比大陸控制係安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" c